data.description: Beautiful 3/2 on a large corner lot, and located in popular eastern area of Lehigh Acres. Volume ceilings, tile, pantry, tons of counter space, garden tub and separate shower in master bath. Recent updates include; new carpet in bedrooms, A/C 4 years old, and well equipment 3 years old. Close to Joel Blvd, Lee, 82, shopping and restaurants. Driveway located on Clayton. Don't miss out. Easy to show.. Seller Motivated.
